rows.name:
You can see a red tree from here, mo.
There's no other vermilion as vibrant as that, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200241_01_msg0002
rows.name: Its name is the Saffronia Tree, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200241_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Haruru wanted to see that tree every day, so
I moved from Avaritia to this Fons Maim,
mo.

rows.label: tlk42200241_01_msg0004
rows.name: Haruru has fallen in love with that tree, mo!
